If you're in the Pasadena area and happen to see this license plate,  
you'll know who's car it is -- mine!  I think I have a lock on the  
state of California, as far as Cantera plates go.  But maybe you live  
somewhere else and want your own personal Cantera license plate (and  
who doesn't?)  All you need to do is contact your local Department of  
Motor Vehicles, fill out lots of forms, pay some unreasonable fee,  
and then wait until they get around to making it...

But hey, it's worth it, right?

Dave
